{
  "text": "While Ph-3 gene, has been incorporated into many breeding lines of fresh market and processing tomato due to its efficacy against broad range of P. insfestans isolates. In recent study, the Ph-3 gene showed highly stability under the field condition unlike Ph-1 or Ph-2 [CITATION_1] ).",
